A cybersecurity company runs a password cracking challenge on a laptop, while a data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance. Recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails, and career counselors advise attendees to maintain eye contact. Additionally, the engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage.

Event staff scan registrations and hand out lanyards at the entrance, while career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops. Career counselors redirect unsure students toward applicable industries. The engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage. Tech companies display demo screens showcasing their latest apps, and a robotics startup flies a small drone above its booth for attention. Recruiters also remind students to follow up with personalized emails. Announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair.

Finance firms offer QR codes for immediate internship applications, while consulting firms stack glossy case study booklets on high tables. Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths. A startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session, and an aroma of coffee and catered snacks spreads from the lounge. Meanwhile, friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly. A welcome announcement outlines the fair schedule over the PA system. As the event concludes, volunteers stack collapsed booths and gather leftover brochures.

A welcome announcement outlining the fair schedule is broadcasted over the PA system. Consulting firms display glossy case study booklets on high tables, and a robotics startup attracts attention with a small drone flying above its booth. Healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos. Small groups of students evaluate which recruiters appeared most enthusiastic, while friends gather on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly. Some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall, and the dean stops by to thank recruiters for their support of the university.
